    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to finance.fixed_asset. Business justification: Fire suppression systems, alarms, and extinguishers are capitalized assets. Linking safety records to asset register enables maintenance cost tracking, depreciation schedules, insurance documentation,' ;
