    rdfs:comment 'The letter grade or pass/fail result assigned by the health inspector during the last inspection. [ENUM-REF-CANDIDATE: A|B|C|Pass|Fail|Satisfactory|Unsatisfactory — 7 candidates stripped; promote to reference product]' ;
